      "date": "2013-04-30 16:09:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/818b4ba0-b1ad-11e2-802d-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  8 tests failed: sanity-hsm, runtests, lustre-rsync-test, sanity-quota, insanity, replay-ost-single, recovery-small, conf-sanity.",
